name: Drag Race Italy
overview: On the Italian version of RuPaul's Drag Race, drag queens compete for the title of Italy's Next Drag Superstar.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: After the great success of the first season, Drag Race Italia is back. On the jury is Priscilla, Chiara Francini and Tommaso Zorzi. Ten drag queens are ready to challenge each other with all the weapons at their disposal: talent, charisma, courage, elegance and extravagance. All the competitors aspire to make it to the final victory: the title of Italy’s Next Drag Superstar.

episodes.name: Ciao Italia
episodes.overview: In the premiere episode of Drag Race Italia, eight Italian queens enter the Werkroom and compete in a classic mini challenge: a photo shoot set in Venice. Then they will be called on to create an Italian style dress to impress the judges on the catwalk.

episodes.name: Divas
episodes.overview: The queens face a very funny mini challenge: limbo! In the maxi challenge, the queens will be tasked with starring in a commercial! On the Main Stage, they will have to give their best with a look that pays homage to great divas.

episodes.name: Night of a Thousand Raffaella Carràs
episodes.overview: The third episode of Drag Race Italia is dedicated to the famous and loved LGBTQIA icon, Raffaella Carrà and includes a Rusical dedicated to her life.

episodes.name: Snatch Game & Fab 80's
episodes.overview: The queens await the arrival of the judges in the Werkroom who share the theme of the mini challenge: Makeup in the Dark. Which of them will be able to do perfect makeup in the dark? And who will be able to do an amazing impersonation in the Snatch Game? On the runway, we take a dip in the fabulous 80’s!

guest_stars.character: Self - Global Senior Artist For MAC Cosmetics
guest_stars.name: Michele Magnani

episodes.name: Long Live the Drag Bride
episodes.overview: For the semi-final, friends and relatives will get makeovers to become drag queens for a night. On the Main Stage, the category is “Long Live the Drag Bride.”

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: In the Finale the four finalists will perform their own original verses to song by RuPaul. After the runway and one last elimination three of them will battle in a lip-sync leading to the coronation of the Italia's First Drag Superstar.

episodes.name: Little Italy
episodes.overview: Ten new drag queens enter the Drag Race Italia Werkroom for a new season. The first episode, dedicated to Italy, will see them try their hand in a sewing test where they will have to pay homage to Italian art. Special guest is legendary icon of Italian music: Patty Pravo!

episodes.name: Colorful Drag, Lucky Drag
episodes.overview: The queens star in a passionate interpretation of a hilarious telenovela rewritten in a drag key, and the runway is dedicated to flowers. Who will be eliminated?

episodes.name: Snatch Game
episodes.overview: The queens participate in Reading is Fundamental and the iconic Snatch Game. Plus, astonishment is the word on the runway. Nothing is as it seems in this episode where anything can happen!

episodes.name: Daughters of the Stars
episodes.overview: Italian passion for stars and esotericism is the theme of this episode. In the mini challenge, the queens will have to face a very particular quiz that will see them as protagonists. In the maxi challenge, they will be improvised fortune tellers with very special customers. On the runway, the queens bring looks inspired by zodiac signs.

episodes.name: Festival Drag
episodes.overview: In a disco-themed episode with a very lively mini-challenge, the Rusical returns, and this time it’s dedicated to a great icon of international music: Lady Gaga. On the runway, the category is: dancing queens.

episodes.name: Sporty Queens
episodes.overview: In this episode, the queens will face a very special makeover test where they will have to transform a football team into fantastic drag queens! Will they succeed? On the runway, they will have to pay homage to the world of sports with a drag touch.

episodes.name: A Walk in Time
episodes.overview: It's time for a roast! With irreverence and a pinch of malice. our queens will have to try to be perfect standup comedians. On the runway, the queens take a journey through time with a series of outfits that pay homage to the various eras of history.

guest_stars.character: Self - Global Senior Artist For MAC Cosmetics
guest_stars.name: Michele Magnani

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: The Grand Finale is here! The finalists will become the first Italian drag band performing their first unreleased track in a singing and dancing challenge. The time has finally come for the coronation. On the runway, the queens must show their most iconic Eleganza Extravaganza. Who will be Italy's Next Drag Superstar?

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: After the great success of the first season, Drag Race Italia is back. On the jury is Priscilla, Chiara Francini and Tommaso Zorzi. Ten drag queens are ready to challenge each other with all the weapons at their disposal: talent, charisma, courage, elegance and extravagance. All the competitors aspire to make it to the final victory: the title of Italy’s Next Drag Superstar.

episodes.name: Express Yourself
episodes.overview: The first episode of the new season leaves room for the creativity and talent of the queens.

episodes.name: Walk of Fame
episodes.overview: The second installment of Drag Race Italia is a tribute to Italian and international cinema.

episodes.name: Night of a Thousand Paola and Chiaras
episodes.overview: The episode of Drag Race Italia is a tribute to the Italian singing couple Paola and Chiara.

episodes.name: The Devil Wears Drag!
episodes.overview: A grand tribute to the glossy world of fashion in all its many facets.

episodes.name: Back to School
episodes.overview: This week the drag queens return to school desks in the role of pupils and teachers.

episodes.name: Snatch Game - Italia Season 3
episodes.overview: In the Snatch Game, drag queens showcase their skills as impersonators of VIPs and celebrities.

episodes.name: A Rhythm of Drag
episodes.overview: To the Rhythm of Drag" is the motto of this episode, devoted entirely to the world of dance.

episodes.name: Death Drags You
episodes.overview: It's roast time, and Drag Race Italy humorously takes on the funereal theme of death.

episodes.name: Social Media Queens
episodes.overview: Drag Race Italia gives a tribute to Generation Z and the new social media trends.
